OL,3,CMan, 87, bundled into car and dumped
OL,4,C15 miles away
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,7,Fafter an 87-year-old man was forced
OL,8,Finto a car, blindfolded, beaten and
OL,9,Fdumped alone 15 miles away.
OL,11,FThe man was walking from Oldham
OL,12,FCentral Mosque between 8pm and 9.30pm
OL,13,Fon Sunday 15 September when the
OL,14,Fincident happened, in what detectives
OL,15,Fare calling a 'terrifying ordeal'.
