OL,3,CMan, 87, bundled into car and dumped
OL,4,C15 miles away
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) say as
OL,7,Fthe man he turned onto Lee Street from
OL,8,FManchester Street in Oldham, a black
OL,9,Fvehicle pulled up beside him, two men
OL,10,Fgot out and forced him into the
OL,11,Fvehicle.
OL,13,FIt is believed the man was then
OL,14,Fblindfolded, with demands being made
OL,15,Ffor money and his phone.
OL,17,FDuring the incident, the man said he
OL,18,Fwas threatened repeatedly, while being
OL,19,Fattacked. Officers say he could have
OL,20,Fbeen killed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
