OL,3,CMan, 87, bundled into car and dumped
OL,4,C15 miles away
OL,6,FThe pensioner was eventually pushed
OL,7,Fout of the car on a dark road, with
OL,8,Fthe vehicle making off.
OL,10,FIt was another hour before he was able
OL,11,Fto find a house, on Oldham Road in
OL,12,FRishworth, to get help call 999, at
OL,13,Faround 10.40pm.
OL,15,FGMP want to speak to two men described
OL,16,Fas being Asian and potentially
OL,17,FBangladeshi, due to speaking the
OL,18,Fvictim's language.
