OL,3,CMan, 87, bundled into car and dumped
OL,4,C15 miles away
OL,6,FThey are described as being
OL,7,Fapproximately 25-30 years old, wearing
OL,8,Ft-shirts and were seen drinking
OL,9,Falcohol from the bottle.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Emma Hulston said:
OL,12,F"This awful attack on an elderly man
OL,13,Fsimply walking down the street is a
OL,14,Fdisturbing act that we are fully
OL,15,Finvestigating.
