OL,3,CMan, 87, bundled into car and dumped
OL,4,C15 miles away
OL,6,F"The victim, who suffered serious
OL,7,Finjuries during the incident, endured
OL,8,Fa terrifying ordeal in which he was
OL,9,Ftaken from close to his home, before
OL,10,Fbeing left with torn clothes in the
OL,11,Fmiddle of a dark road in unfamiliar
OL,12,Fsurroundings, and with no means of
OL,13,Fcommunication.
OL,15,F"We are fortunate we are not talking
OL,16,Fabout a potentially more serious or
OL,17,Feven fatal outcome."
